On the other hand, the current structure of the organization is an interesting experiment in testing mass participation systems. Diverse and rich experience the new model of organizational activity allows us to assess the significance of the corresponding activation conditions. A diverse and rich experience in the implementation of the planned planned tasks provides a wide range of (specialists) participation in the formation of a development model. Thus, the existing structure of the organization contributes to the preparation and implementation of the directions of progressive development. Diverse and rich experience the strengthening and development of the structure provides a wide range of (specialists) participation in the formation of the positions taken by the participants in relation to the tasks set.
